<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="description-n">description <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'skrɪpʃn/    美 /dɪ'skrɪpʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 描写；描述；形容；叙述：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He gave us a <strong>brief description</strong> of the accident. 
他向我们简单地描述了那次事故的经过。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="beyond-description">beyond description</h3>
<p>1.<strong>难以描述；难以形容：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The grand sight of Mount Huangshan is beyond description. 
黄山的壮丽美景难以形容。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The book gives a short <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (描述) of the city.   （2007 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. description  </p></div>